title: Eurythmics - Boxed (2005) & Unboxed (2008)
description:
EURYTHMICS: 9 CD Box Set ''Boxed'' (2005):

Original studio albums:
* In The Garden (1982)
* Sweet Dreams (Are Made Of This) (1983)
* Touch (1983)
* Be Yourself Tonight (1985)
* Revenge (1986)
* Savage (1987)
* We Too Are One (1989)

* 43 Bonus Tracks

+

''Unboxed'' (2008):
* Touch Dance (1984)

* Rough & Tough At The Roxy (1986)
* Eurythmics Live 1983-1989 (1993)
* Peacetour (2000)
* Greatest Hits (1991)
* The Ultimate Collection (2005)
* Unboxed 12'' Essentials (2008)
